data.title: Biografi Lionel Messi
data.meta_description:
Biografi Lionel Messi - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The brief biography summarizes Lionel Messi as: 

1) Lionel Messi is an Argentine football player who currently plays as a striker for Spanish club Barcelona. 2) He was born in Rosario, Argentina and joined Barcelona's youth academy at age 13 after being denied treatment for a hormone deficiency by his local club. 3) Messi has won numerous titles with Barcelona including multiple La Liga and Champions League trophies, and individual awards including being named FIFA World Player of the Year a record six times.
